Network based intrusion detection system using Machine Learning 

How to run the project

Requirements
- python
- install dependencies = pip install -r requirements.txt

Run Random_Forest_Compare.py to see the comparison of both models used 
Logistic Regression and Random Forest 
- python src/Random_Forest_Compare.py

Save the models using save_model.py, before running the GUI
- python src/save_model.py
this saves the random_forest_model.pkl and preprocess.pkl inside the models folder.

Finally run GUI
- python src/GUI_App.py

